title: Gamemodes help
body:
Im trying to play some team builder (for example) or twisted treeline ranked but the game modes are simply not there, and even the ones that are usually there like ranked teams ping in and out of existence, is there a reason for this or am I just glitched?

I {{champion:86}}tee this isn't my fault
If team builder isn't coming back... {{champion:6}} to be kidding me

replies.body: Teambuilder was removed a couple weeks ago by Riot (on OCE) and Ranked TT has never even been on OCE. If you want the times queues are up, check this: http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/ZzQR1haM-queue-schedule-updated
